&lt;p style=&quot; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;In these notes, written on a letter bearing the remnants of its red seal wax, Newton calculated, based on the Book of Daniel 7:25, that the end of time will arrive in the year &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;2060&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;.&amp;#160; Newton&apos;s calculations relied on his belief that the starting point is the year 800, a time when Charlemagne founded the Holy Roman Empire and the Pope&apos;s supremacy commenced. Here, Newton believed, &amp;#160;began the period of the &quot;apostate&apos;s&quot; church deepest corruption which will end in the Apocalyptic events &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color: black;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;such as plagues and fires, the terrible battle of Armageddon and eternal damnation of the wicked &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;mentioned in the&amp;#160; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color: black;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;Book of Revelation.&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt; 
