&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top: 0.07in; margin-bottom: 0.02in; margin-left: 0.12in;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt;After the war was over the Scroll was returned to the few survivors of the community, and the honorary president of the community, Mr. Moshe Sauriano gave them to the Benatar family, to be brought to the NLI, in memory of the Jews from Rhodes who were exterminated.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

