&lt;p class=&quot;defaultstyle&quot; dir=&quot;LTR&quot;&gt;In 1942 Yahuda received a position in the New School of Social Research in New-York, and from then on, until his death in 1951, spent most of his time on his research.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
