&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: &apos;Gentium Plus&apos;;&quot;&gt;The Crucifixion of Jesus and the two thieves, the two Marys standing under the cross, Jesus being taken down from the Cross and buried, and the Resurrection.&amp;#160;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

