&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;LTR&quot;&gt;Written between 1300-1350 in Spain, it is the most splendid illuminated copy known. Although copied in Spain, most of the illustrations were done in Perugia&amp;#160; Italy around 1400 in the studio of Matteo di Ser Cambio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt;&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
