&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: 12.0pt;&quot;&gt;King Solomon&apos;s palace and the First Temple depicted in detail: The Temple Courtyard drawn according to Josephus&apos; description, the Ark and the Cherubim, the High Priest, the Candelabrum and the Table of the Showbread, as well as the Sacrificial Altar in front of the Temple.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt; 
