&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size: 12.0pt;&quot;&gt;Abraham&apos;s Death: Abraham is being lowered into the grave in the Cave of the Makhpela to be buried beside Sarah. (Genesis 25)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&gt;&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;&gt;
