&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 25.45pt; margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin-left: 0cm; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;The most captivating feature in this map are the picture emblems which tell the story of Abraham:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Abraham&apos;s family led by Abraham and his father Terah, are commanded by God to leave Haran for the Promised Land (Genesis 11:31).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

